<div class="jumbotron" style="background: url('{{resPath}}/images/r_bg_coins.jpg') no-repeat center center; background-size: cover;">
  <div class="topLeft"><h1>SMSwallet</h1></div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <img src="{{resPath}}/images/x_hero_phones.png">
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h2>No borders or barriers, just send an SMS.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Send and receive bitcoin anywhere in the world via SMS. No internet or smartphone required.</p>
      <label>Sign-up to be an SMSwallet beta user.</label>
      <input id="searchInput" type="tel" name="search" class="form-control" placeholder="+XXYYYYYYYY" disabled>
      <div class="inputDesc"><label>Country</label><label>Mobile Number</label></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h2>SMSwallet Commands</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <p>After setting up your account, you will receive an automated text message from a gateway. To control your account, send any of these commands to that phone number via SMS, no smartphone or internet required.</p>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">Become an SMSwallet beta user</div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <a class="btn btn-default" href="#gateways">Open a Wallet &raquo;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <table class="table table-striped">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Command</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>HELP</td><td>List available commands</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PIN</td><td>Setup spending PIN</td></tr>
        <tr><td>BAL</td><td>See balance in mBTC</td></tr>
        <tr><td>SEND</td><td>Send bitcoins to phone number, bitcoin address.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>TRANS</td><td>List the last 3 transactions</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row blue">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h2>SMSgateways</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <p>Decentralized, open-source Android app that bridges between SMS and Bitcoin for low-end Android phones. In other words, connect any country to the global economy.</p>
    <p>Gateways are operated by partners who earn transaction fees. To become an SMSgateway partner, the following are required:<ul>
    <li>Dedicated Android phone</li>
    <li>Text messaging plan</li>
    <li>Internet connection</li></ul></p>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">Become an SMSgateway partner</div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <a class="btn btn-default" href="#gateways">Open a Gateway &raquo;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 intl-tel-input">
    <table class="table table-hover">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><i class="fa fa-flag"></i></th>
          <th>Number</th>
          <th>Fee</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="gwTable">
        
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>